{"tid":2215543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Foodpanda派黃店四喜月餅比外送員，疑似藍屍外賣仔一野整爛佢","createTime":"2020-09-24T05:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T18:49:55.000Z","uid":162944,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dd74b9c46ae10247469c2910fc87f7891d513fc8","tid":2215543,"uid":162944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:14:20.000Z","msg":"話說今年Foodpanda同本地黃店四喜搞聯乘晌pandamart賣, send email同客戶力sell四喜月餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxqG4jo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxqG4jo.png&h=bca74985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MU8Ksx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MU8Ksx.png&h=9fe40780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayheybakery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayheybakery&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=8f84e486\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayheybakery</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sayhey4cake/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsayhey4cake%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=67399d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sayhey4cake/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個都要$60, 唔平架, 仲要已經賣斷市<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MREphKp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMREphKp.png&h=d3f3638b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且仲訂左幾萬個月餅連雨傘電風扇晌中秋派比後勤員工同外送員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iy7ya0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiy7ya0a.png&h=de420687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8OUTVvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8OUTVvn.jpg&h=c9a1d7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知有疑似藍屍on9外賣仔認為係三無月餅，唔單止拍片將個月餅整到變屎餅，仲叫其他外送員唔好去拎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MPTVs1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MPTVs1.png&h=c56a822a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLP1jUR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLP1jUR.png&h=0bd057a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGH6v1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGH6v1L.jpg&h=2ae38490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L61V8Pu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL61V8Pu.png&h=16b299aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31CeEWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31CeEWa.png&h=31e4f607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係屌喇星，幾多人想買都買唔到，非洲小朋友仲食緊樹皮咋，人地老細都做唔切比預訂左既客，而家你一野就整爛人地老闆心血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEEXCMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEEXCMN.png&h=3e7fc038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41fc9e131ba6a37f25762389bb163a066fbc229f","tid":2215543,"uid":58335,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"所以條死藍屍咪做死一世外賣仔囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ad7da6966b54a0df7fabcb109f0aca501c676c","tid":2215543,"uid":373119,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"其實乜野係三無品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7252c5a8b85c2f14a241da93166014b2723146c","tid":2215543,"uid":162944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q_kpUdU68TM