c133e3dc","tid":2215543,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"8052c9673995102419dc474958d80b0f29c97773","tid":2215543,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻鳩四喜今年現貨得9月30號有得賣 賣得一日... 你唔預訂去拿貨都冇得你食 on99"},{"pid":"bd1254147acec790c659277d8290a606f44a49aa","tid":2215543,"uid":316329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"唔要就咪撚拎啦垃圾"},{"pid":"c89b633306352a2f8df7c3dfa735f3cea77f5b8c","tid":2215543,"uid":350163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"洗白關公你好，你又話閪熊買左幾萬個，點睇3萬個外賣員，半日唔洗就話就黎冇哂？做關公show都有誠意少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要屈送外賣全部藍屍？我屌你啦，平時點壓炸小店呀閪熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因反應熱烈，月餅已剩餘少量。當所有月餅派發完畢，隨後合資格的送遞員仍能領取foodpanda電風扇或雨傘。如你仍未有機會前往尖沙咀辦公室領取，26/09/2020（星期六） 為最後一天（1000-1230 及 1400-1630）。請注意，這次是以先到先得形式派發，派完即止。<br />\n<br />\n注意健康，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\nFollowing an overwhelming response, we now only have limited quantities of mooncakes. Once all the mooncakes are distributed, all following eligible couriers will still be able to receive our foodpanda fan or umbrella upon collection. If you did not have any chance to visit our TST office, kindly note that 26/09/2020 (Saturday)  will be the last collection day (1000-1230 &amp; 1400-1630) and please be reminded that this distribution is on a first come first served basis, collection will be closed once all the<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> items have been distributed. <br />\n<br />\nStay healthy, thank you."}]}